{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/PageBanner_Brimstone.png?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brimstone Brawlers is a fast-paced multiplayer brawler set in a grim, industrial fantasy world where chaos reigns and mayhem thrives. Step into the dark, twisted city of Brimstone, a place where the lines between magic and technology blur, and every corner hides new dangers.<br><br>Choose from a diverse cast of morally ambiguous characters\u2014each with unique abilities and playstyles. Engage in frantic, skill-based combat, where every brawl is a test of strategy and reflexes. Unleash devastating attacks, master the battlefield, and outmaneuver your enemies in chaotic arenas that pulse with deadly hazards and shifting environments.<br><br>Whether you're teaming up with friends or battling foes solo, every match in Brimstone Brawlers is a blend of tactical depth and explosive action. It\u2019s easy to pick up, but the depth lies in mastering your character\u2019s abilities and outsmarting your opponents in intense, arena-based combat.<br><br>Are you ready to brawl in a city where anything goes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/TrainWide4.gif?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/Title_Arenas.png?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set in a fantasy Lovecraftian industrial world, brawls occur in a variety of dangerous hazard-filled 3d arenas. Laugh in delight as you knock a friend off to their doom or scream in fear as you get hit by a runaway train!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/Bamball.gif?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/Title_Gamemodes.png?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brawl against friends in a variety of different PvP modes including Free For All Deathmatch, Free For All Stock, Team Deathmatch and Team Stock. For a change of pace players can play the bonus mode Bamball, Brimstone\u2019s take on football, where they can use their abilities to disrupt (or eliminate) their opponents before scoring the winning goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/Title_Brawlers.png?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from an initial cast of five Brawlers with unique abilities and playstyles including the bombastic explosive-maniac Bomber, a deranged Plague Doctor who thinks he is an actual bird, and the menacing Vampire just looking for love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/Brawlers_Core.png?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/Title_Multiplayer.png?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with up to four friends locally with controllers or play online with up to eight players through peer-to-peer connections.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/Title_Soundtrack.png?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stellar industrial victorian soundtrack by Andy Gillion (solo artist, songwriter and lead guitarist of Mors Principium Est) provides the perfect atmosphere to brawl with friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Target Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/b248d1da470343a4e6fab904b8197b518de403fb.jpg"},{"name":"Target Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/e2f2ddf1da7a8870a3822bb8e6a5fc4002709a64.jpg"},{"name":"Target Rookie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/7b80d3543396d58f747febca4aa8e9f5f997346e.jpg"},{"name":"Beach Bash","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/5f0663e833fd8c7c699ed23d83b0e32689485f06.jpg"},{"name":"\"Glove\"","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/e37458bc31a2e27b76f89cb4f73da5b3866dd31f.jpg"},{"name":"Rookie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/167f2f4069aa1efcc13db9feb2622116e1b363fc.jpg"},{"name":"Scrapper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/d54d36cd91b24ff4168ee4c5ac50b112ff98ec3e.jpg"},{"name":"Combatant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/d1b7c7983f1bd44360c133eb653e833ca5257576.jpg"},{"name":"Ruffian","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/bcc4534bc221fd12a1bbd372469b6ab3b3685000.jpg"},{"name":"Bruiser","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/780270/087b16d2ecabd7f01c6dedeca8f44b43d156ce47.jpg"}],"total":26},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732614082","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732614082","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamsta