tiplayer.png?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with up to four friends locally with controllers or play online with up to eight players through peer-to-peer connections.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/extras/Title_Soundtrack.png?t=1732614082\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stellar industrial victorian soundtrack by Andy Gillion (solo artist, songwriter and lead guitarist of Mors Principium Est) provides the perfect atmosphere to brawl with friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Ategig"],"dlc":[1338700],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/780270/header.jpg?t=1732614082","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257076624,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257076624/movie480.mp4?t=1732593270","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257076624/movie_max.mp4?t=1732593270"},"name":"Early Access Gameplay","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257076624/9d15ed5580ca6b4d2cf5a7a730604f5b38682ae9/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1732593270","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257076624/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1732593270","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257076624/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1732593270"}}],"name":"Brimstone Brawlers - Early Access","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> 64-bit Windows 7, Windows 8.1, Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i5-4430 / AMD FX-6300<